̉a mình để phát triển một phần mềm mới, thành lập công ty của riêng mình. Từ đây, các vấn đề xoay quanh hôn nhân gia đình và tài chính bắt đầu xảy ra. Liệu những điều này có thể gây ảnh hưởng đến cuộc hôn nhân của hai người họ hay không?</p>","tmdb":{"type":"tv","id":"127588","season":1,"vote_average":8.6,"vote_count":26},"modified":"2023-09-05T02:46:56.000Z","cast":["Burcu Özberk","İlhan Şen","Mehmet Korhan Fırat","Günay Karacaoğlu","Zeynep Kankonde","Ceren Koç","Mehmet Yilmaz","Suleyman Atanisev","Sevda Baş"],"director":["Murat Ozturk"],"cast_meta":[{"name":"Burcu Özberk","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Burcu Özberk","tmdb_id":1522700,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/wDhKUUR7pRzgVolACed0YnSozbL.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1522700"},{"name":"İlhan Şen","name_vi":null,"name_original":"İlhan Şen","tmdb_id":2510156,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/hfXuzYYr0QfHsGrI6eu2wrE63jM.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2510156"},{"name":"Mehmet Korhan Fırat","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Mehmet Korhan Fırat","tmdb_id":1992177,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/87Lri6GuddVrTOcy1Bi9ofcHx9m.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1992177"},{"name":"Günay Karacaoğlu","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Günay Karacaoğlu","tmdb_id":1884711,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/89R4B8WVYcWV4LARoutb9nABMKf.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1884711"},{"name":"Zeynep Kankonde","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Zeynep Kankonde","tmdb_id":1463936,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/jimRmLKus5HS5Gv9H0stQzF36yC.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1463936"},{"name":"Ceren Koç","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Ceren Koç","tmdb_id":2031280,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/9J22BHhT7kgFknHnP1YLb7VmzGI.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2031280"},{"name":"Mehmet Yilmaz","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Mehmet Yilmaz","tmdb